    <p>This piece was de­signed in 1984 by Nor­we­gian de­signer Peter Opsvik for Flokk, Europe’s lead­ing man­u­fac­turer of qual­ity seat­ing fur­ni­ture.</p>
    <p>The sad­dle seat can be ad­justed be­tween low and high work­ing po­si­tions – all the way up to a stand­ing po­si­tion – en­abling the user to be more dy­namic in move­ment while still seated in a bal­anced po­si­tion.</p>
    <p>Price: $1,985 to $2,860 at W. Ate­lier</p>

